[The community deaths do not appear to be decreasing. Until the members of the community change where individuals go to the Ebola treatment centers for medical care when they are sick, Ebola will continue to spread. Proper PPE is lacking in the community centers, and safe burials are not likely to be regularly performed. - Mod.LK]

